vote.title: A resolution authorizing an increase in the joint election agreement and election services contract between the City of Dallas and Dallas County for the May 4, 2024 special (bond) election in the amount of $76,060.08, from $595,279.67 to $671,339.75 - Not to exceed $76,060.08 - Financing: General Fund
